search:dotnet+core:asp.net core minimal.content:
- **CLI Commands**:
  - `dotnet new webapi -n MyMinimalApiApp`
  - `dotnet add package Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.NewtonsoftJson`
  - `dotnet add package Swashbuckle.AspNetCore`

- **Latest Versions**:
  - ASP.NET Core: 6.0
  - Swagger/OpenAPI: 6.0

- **Key Config Options**:
  - In `Program.cs`:
    ```csharp
    builder.Services.AddEndpointsApiExplorer();
    builder.Services.AddSwaggerGen(c =>
    {
        c.SwaggerDoc("v1", new OpenApiInfo { Title = "MyMinimalApiApp", Version = "v1" });
    });

    app.UseSwagger();
    app.UseSwaggerUI(c => c.SwaggerEndpoint("/swagger/v1/swagger.json", "MyMinimalApiApp v1"));
    ```
